# game/Scenes/Welch/welch2.rpy:21
translate chinese welch2a_867ebba2:

    # sst "I don't usually do this, because I don't want my students to feel like they are forced to participate."
    sst "我平时不这么做，因为不想让学生觉得是被迫参加的。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch2.rpy:22
translate chinese welch2a_0079d33b:

    # sst "So please don't feel like you're forced. It won't reflect on my opinion of you or your grade in this class if you decline."
    sst "所以请别觉得是被强迫的。如果你拒绝，这不会影响我对你的看法，也不会影响你这门课的成绩。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch2.rpy:23
translate chinese welch2a_e59995d6:

    # sst "But since you helped me with the voter registration, I wanted to invite you to a protest tonight."
    sst "但既然你帮我做了选民登记，我想邀请你参加今晚的抗议活动。"

